---
description: A template for answering questions about a dialog (user prompt)
author: Calvin Ku
version: 1.0.0
---

<instruction>
<dialogue>
{% for turn in dialogue_turns %}
**{{ turn.speaker }}:** {{ turn.text }}
{% endfor %}
</dialogue>

<question>
{{ question_text }}

<answer_choices>
{% for choice in choices %}
{{ loop.index0 }}. {{ choice }}
{% endfor %}
</answer_choices>
</question>

<output_format>
Please analyze the dialogue above and answer each question. Provide your response in JSON format.

For each question, provide:
1. A short description of what was discussed in the conversation
2. A brief explanation of your reasoning
3. The index of the answer choice that you selected
</output_format>
</instruction>